Text: 'I''m basically belongs to army family.

  My father retired as a Sub Major.

  While my father is in army whole life they transfer to different locations of India
  & along with we are also travel all beautiful cities.

  From the bigning of our childhood we saw lots of different geographical location.

  Now we l go with our friends for trips.

  It''s last year when we plan to visit Manali. It''s really amazing to be there for
  3 days. We enjoyed a lot. We met lots of foreign . India is very friendly country.
  Everyone wants to help you, even they don''t know your language.'
